<div class="w3-content w3-container w3-padding-64" id="app">
  
  <h3 class="w3-center">THE BECKENHAM PLACE PARK SOUNDWALK</h3>
  <p class="w3-center"><em>Soundlab presents:</em><br />
    The Beckenham Place Park Soundwalk</p>
  <p  class="w3-center">SoundLab has created a free app to take you on an
  immersive soundwalk around Beckenham Place Park. It is based on stories
  gathered and shared by locals. </p>
  
  <div class="w3-row-padding w3-center">
    <div class="w3-col w3-half">
      <img src="img/app-phone.png" width="80%" alt="BPP Soundwalk App" />
      <br />
    </div>
