	Download the app free from the <a
	href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.bpp.sound.walk&rdid=org.bpp.sound.walk" target="_blank">Google Play Store</a> and
	<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bpp-soundwalk/id1268630589" target="_blank">iTunes</a>.
      </h5>
      <h5>Featuring:</h5>
      <ul class="w3-left-align">
	<li>9 sonic memories of Beckenham Place Park</li>
	<li>Interactive buttons to control the audio players</li>
	<li>Automatic triggering of audio using GPS</li>
	<li>Free download</li>
	<li>How-to-use audio instructions on the Mansion button</li>
	<li>Help and credits sections</li>
	<li>Beautiful bespoke design</li>
	<li>Seekable playbars</li>
      </ul>
